# This file is an EXAMPLE only. The real `passwd` is generated on the box,
# not committed to git (see ../../.gitignore — entry: stack/mosquitto/passwd).
#
# Format (one user per line):
#   <username>:<hash>
#
# Generate the real file with mosquitto_passwd inside the running container:
#
#   docker exec -it mosquitto mosquitto_passwd -c -b /mosquitto/config/passwd \
#     "$MQTT_USER" "$MQTT_PASSWORD"
#
# Or use the helper script: bash setup.sh
#
# Example (DO NOT use this hash — it's just to show the shape):
# plant:$7$101$abcd...$xyz...
